== Flotilla commanders ==
* ''[[Fregattenkapitan]]'' Hermann Rigele (April 1944&ndash;March 1945) 
* ''[[Korvettenkapitän]]'' [[Ulrich Heyse]] (March&ndash;May 1945)

==Assigned U-boats==
Forty-three U-boats were assigned to this flotilla during its service.
